<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-07-09 19:10:09.410937</lastBuildDate><item><title>Grandpa’s reaction to grandsons 3D printer</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pz0Kdzr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mqBy5vG.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2QAqHLG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pz0Kdzr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vidadobl6]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Went to Planned Parenthood for the yearly</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/p740JtY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6qAVibr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And man. I just cannot underscore how amazing it was. Got a mammogram scheduled, got an IUD inserted, got an appointment with a menopause doctor. Issues I’ve been discussing for years with my GP were addressed THEN. Like, at the appointment. Immediately. I had no idea IUD was an option for me. I had no idea there were doctors who focus on peri menopause & menopause. I WISH my regular doctor were even half as interested in my well being as this doctor was. 

AND There’s a literal Plan B vending machine outside. Chef’s kiss.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O3HOygA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I first went to PP when I was 15. They were my hero then, and 32 years later they still rock.  In closing: Got reproductive organs? Even old ones? Go to Planned Parenthood if it’s an option in your area. They bill insurance, give excellent care, & you get to support something important. #plannedparenthood #abortionishealthcare #fuckyouscotus</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/p740JtY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mbcb350]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fetterman!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8BjQ1Af</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hkB6lD6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#Fetterman</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8BjQ1Af</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[codenametrixie]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Kavanaugh is trending and the posts are on point</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/go46xrU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jgcEDNs.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/go46xrU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CaptainInvictus]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So true</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lyM0ofP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/45yiEp1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lyM0ofP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[FuriousNinjaBread]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I build fake products and today I created the Jewel Cooler.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/B01JoPD</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IjshQgb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div>